CreateStream

Create a Stream

HTTP Request

POST \2010-04-01\Accounts\{AccountSid}\Calls\{CallSid}\Streams.json HTTP/1.1

host: api.twilio.com:443
accept: application/json
content-type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

Parameters

AccountSid [ in: path type: string ]
The SID of the Account that created this Stream resource. required
CallSid [ in: path type: string ]
The SID of the Call the Stream resource is associated with. required
